[SN]TITLE[SN]
Arbroath flat targeted twice by thieves

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Police are hunting thieves who targeted an Arbroath flat twice in the space of two days.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The raiders stole house keys, a computer tablet and a mobile phone from the St Vigeans Road flat between 18:00 on Tuesday and 07:30 on Wednesday.
Thieves then returned to steal four gent's watches from the same property at about 01:00 on Thursday.
Officers have appealed for anyone who was in the area at the time to come forward.
